
EVB method 

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Project folder structure:
	- scan -> 	THIS FILES WILL BE CREATED BY EVB_AGENT.JAVA
			scan_*.xyz files of every scan point
			scan_data.txt: it includes state 1 and 2 numbers
			scan.csv: R, Eg, Eshift
			charges_state1.txt
			charges_state2.txt
	- dl_field -> 	\lib
			dl_field
			dl_f_path1
			dl_f_path2
			state1.control
			state2.control
	- state1 ->	CONTROL 
			DLPOLY.Z										
	- state2 ->	CONTROL 
			DLPOLY.Z
	- mods ->	MoDs_mpi
			- Working_dir -> MoDS_inputs.xml
			- Initial
	- validation ->	CONTROL
			DLPOLY.Z
	
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ALGORITHM:
1) The agent retrive the information from OntoPES
2) It creates the topology files 
3) It calculates E1 and E2
4) It runs MoDS to find EVB parameters

